<template>
  <n-config-provider :theme="darkTheme">
    <n-global-style />
    <n-result status="403" title="503 服务器娘挂了哦" description="要不要听听歌呢">
      <template #footer>
        <n-button key="aplayer" @click="menuClick">找点乐子吧</n-button>
      </template>
    </n-result>
  </n-config-provider>
</template>
<script>
import { darkTheme } from "naive-ui";

export default {
  methods: {
    menuClick(e) {
      // 路由跳转
      this.$router.push(e.key);
    },
  },
  setup() {
    return {
      darkTheme,
    };
  },
};
</script>
